-> **NOTE:** Valid roles are ADMINISTRATOR, SITE_ADMIN, AUTOMATOR, DEPLOYER, ADVISOR, OBSERVER, OPERATIONAL_OBSERVER, SHARED_ADVISOR and SHARED_OBSERVER.

